Forex,API,Convert,Real,Time,Value,from,xignite,converts,an,amount,from,one,currency,to,another,using,the,real,time,rate,If,the,real,time,rate,is,not,available,for,a,currency,pair,e,g,on,a,weekend,then,the,most,recent,available,rate,is,used,Over,historical,and,real,time,currency,pairs,are,covered,The,API,uptime,is,at,least,and,the,data,is,updated,in,true,real,time,as,new,quotes,are,issued,from,market,participants,Data,is,returned,in,XML,JSON,or,CSV,format